#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:1
msgid "Domain Guides"
msgstr "ドメイン別ガイド"

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:3
msgid "Spec-Craft supports multiple creative production domains."
msgstr "Spec-Craftは、複数のクリエイティブ制作ドメインをサポートしています。"

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:5
msgid "Manga Production"
msgstr "漫画制作"

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:6
msgid ""
"Define your storyboard in Obsidian. Use the `trigger_svg_build` tool to "
"inject dialogue from your strategy into SVG templates."
msgstr ""
"Define your storyboard in Obsidian. Use the `trigger_svg_build` tool to "
"inject dialogue from your strategy into SVG templates."

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:7
msgid "**Strategy**: YAML metadata in Obsidian."
msgstr "**Strategy**: YAML metadata in Obsidian."

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:8
msgid "**Tactics**: Translated SVGs in the `build/` directory."
msgstr "**Tactics**: Translated SVGs in the `build/` directory."

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:10
msgid "CAD Modeling (JSCAD)"
msgstr "CAD モデリング (JSCAD)"

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:11
msgid ""
"Specify geometric requirements in Obsidian. Use `trigger_cad_build` to "
"generate JSCAD code and export STL files."
msgstr ""
"Specify geometric requirements in Obsidian. Use `trigger_cad_build` to "
"generate JSCAD code and export STL files."

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:12
msgid ""
"**Visual Feedback**: AI can analyze generated SVGs to \"see\" the model's"
" dimensions."
msgstr ""
"**Visual Feedback**: AI can analyze generated SVGs to \"

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:14
msgid "3D Scene Construction (Blender)"
msgstr "3D シーン構築 (Blender)"

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:15
msgid ""
"Describe tray landscapes (Bonkei) in Obsidian. Use "
"`generate_blender_script` to create Python scripts for Blender."
msgstr ""
"Describe tray landscapes (Bonkei) in Obsidian. Use "
"`generate_blender_script` to create Python scripts for Blender."

#: ../../source/domain-guides.md:16
msgid "**Process**: Obsidian Spec → Blender Python Script → Automated 3D Build."
msgstr "**Process**: Obsidian Spec → Blender Python Script → Automated 3D Build."

